BUCYRUS JOURNALfounded in 1830 Published continuous y since 1867 by John Hopley and Bons The real name of the writer must appear with all sommunications printed in this paper The Telegraph nceepta advertiaing with the rear tain of the leargest paid daily efreelaties at any daily paper in Crewferd County ROBERT E WARD FOREIGN ADV Maaager Brunswick Building ITS Fifth Ave New York Room 1300 NO 6 South Wabash Ave Chicago Ill Single Copy Delivered by carrier per week Wabash Ave Chicago Ill S cents IS cents By Mail outside Crawford County per year 1600 By Mall an Crawford County per year 400 By Mall Bucyrus Weekly Journal per year 160 PBLEPHONESOFFICE tilt NEWS room lira bone 5888 Telegraph Subscribers will greatly facilitate good delivery service by making stl complaints to the business office Not to carriers BUCYAUS OHIO 18009 ON TIB LINCOLN HIGHWAY ANDSCIOTO FRAIL Fill DAV XTOBEI N 19720 OHIO WEATHER"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-04-13T08:13:00.846Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn87076601/1920-10-08/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_goyle_ver01:data:sn87076601:0051699387A:1920100801:0370/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=404&w=317", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_goyle_ver01:data:sn87076601:0051699387A:1920100801:0370/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=808&w=635", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_goyle_ver01/data/sn87076601/0051699387A/1920100801/0370.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["crawford county", "bucyrus", "ohio", "crawford", "united states"], "location_city": ["bucyrus"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["crawford"], "location_state": ["ohio"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "applicati